lastfm.summary: "Prisencolinensinainciusol" is a song composed and performed by Adriano Celentano. The American-English sounding lyrics are actually pure gibberish. A very popular performance of the song, broadcasted by RAI, shows Celentano with showgirl Raffaella Carrà, who is dancing and lip-synching to Mori's vocals. It was first released as a single on November 3, 1972, and later on his album Nostalrock.
